\begin_inset Formula $x,y\in\overline{\Omega}$
\end_inset

 with 
\begin_inset Formula $x\not=y$
\end_inset

 is called 
\emph on
Green's function
\emph default
 for the domain 
\begin_inset Formula $\Omega$
\end_inset

 if the following conditions are satisfied:
